[http://jewwatch.com '''Jew Watch'''] is an archive of TRUTH run by Frank Weltner, a brave man who simply wants to [[Jews did WTC|spread the truth]]. Jew Watch has factual evidence of thousands of atrocities committed by filthy [[kike]]s, past and present, and naturally, this [[butthurt|pisses off]] the Jews to no end.

== The Website ==
[[Jews]], as we all know, have total control over [[media|almost all]] the information in the world. They want John Q. Public to believe that [[forced meme|Jews are honest, nice, hardworking people who are wrongfully persecuted]], and anyone who says different is a Neo-[[Nazi]] scumbag who deserves to die. But Frank Weltner, who can suck a fuck, decided he wanted to change all that and expose the ignorant public to the things the Jews don't want them to know about; such as the fact that Jews have no penises.

== The Google Incident==
Jew Watch grew in popularity, and one day, Steven Weinstock discovered that when he typed Jew into [[Google]], the first website to come up was Jew Watch. Steven flew into a violent rage and desperately tried to get Jew Watch shut down, and to petition Google to move the page down, even though Google constantly explained that pages are ranked automatically based on page views. Over 100,000 [[gay|intelligent]] people signed Weinstock's petition, and it did nothing but create more publicity for Jew Watch and make Weinstock look like a [[faggot|hero]].

== Wikipedia ==
[[The Wikipedia Jews|The Jews on Wikipedia]] have labeled Jew Watch as a neo-nazi [[hate]] site, filled the article with all sorts of other [[lie]]s and exaggerations, and locked the article, a fine example of Wikipedia's policy of "neutrality."

